      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Culture&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Vision&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Communism&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt; &lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Mission&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Realizing the Ideals of the Party, Robust Leadership and Strong Governance. Contributing to World Peace and Development&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt; &lt;/td&gt;
