          &lt;td&gt;Car for Transportation&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Domestic Red flag, dedicated to leaders&amp;rsquo; military parade&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt; &lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Animal&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;The Chinese dragon, forbidden city&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
