          &lt;td&gt;Chairman of CPC&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt; &lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Book&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Marxism–Leninism, Mao Zedong Thought, socialism with Chinese characteristics, Deng Xiaoping Theory. &lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt; &lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Theory system&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;Socialism with Chinese characteristics, Socialist patriotism, Chinese nationalism&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
